 Talk about creative tension in the workplace: Tony Wong of San Gabriel came 
upon a parking lot in which each space was marked "30 Min. Parking" as well as 
"Employee Parking." miscelLAny: 
</P>
<P>
 Jack Schlomer of La Canada Flintridge points out that Lake Arrowhead is the 
home of the Deer Lick Carwash. Wonder if it that process scratches the paint? 
