<HEADLINE>
<P>
CITY HAD NO RIGHT TO IMPOSE RULES ON MOTELS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 I attended the City Council hearings that you reported on in your story "City 
Imposes Tough Rules on 3 Van Nuys Motels," (Oct. 27). 
</P>
<P>
 You failed to point out the major issues and complaints expressed by the motel 
owners, their lawyers and those persons (myself included) who testified on 
their behalf: 
</P>
