<TEXT>
<P>
 Here's how the Buffalo Bills will win the Super Bowl: They will beat New 
England this weekend and Indianapolis next weekend to qualify for the playoffs. 
Then they travel to San Diego and beat the fast-fading Chargers the first 
week.Next they travel back to Miami (whom they own) and beat the Dolphins the 
