<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA121794-0129 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 108948 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
December 17, 1994, Saturday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part A; Page 1; Column 6; Metro Desk 
</P>
