packs, patrol the resort four times a week. Patrols began after Thanksgiving. 
</P>
<P>
 "Unfortunately, the perception has been extremely negative and, the new 
program has led people to believe that there is a crime problem at Snowmass Ski 
Area, which simply is not the case," Police Chief Art Smythe said Thursday. 
