<P>
CAMPO, HODGES, ARIZA EARN CITY'S TOP HONORS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Chatsworth High setter Karla Campo and middle blocker Jennifer Hodges were 
named City Section 4-A Division girls' volleyball players of the year. The 
seniors led the Chancellors to the City championship with a five-game victory 
over Palisades last month. 
</P>
<P>
 Senior outside hitter Mayra Ariza of Sylmar, who led the Spartans to the 3-A 
title, was named the 3-A player of the year. 
</P>
