<HEADLINE>
<P>
BOOTH, PARSONS ADVANCE AT AUSTRALIAN SURF EVENT 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Jeff Booth of Laguna Beach scored the most points Friday in the second round 
of the Coke Surf Classic at North Narrabeen, Australia. 
</P>
<P>
 Booth scored 28.51 points. 
</P>
<P>
 Mike Parsons of San Clemente also advanced to the third round of the Assn. of 
Surfing Professionals world tour event. 
</P>
</TEXT>
