<P>
 Moon exploration -- Because of a copy editing error, a Friday story describing 
new findings about the moon contained the phrase, "the dark side of the moon 
that always turns its back to Earth." Contrary to popular perceptions, the moon 
has no dark side; however, it does have a side permanently facing away from 
Earth. 
